Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.10,0:00:02.26,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,What was it that you needed?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.64,0:00:04.89,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,A little glass of water please
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.08,0:00:07.29,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,A fresh pressed hanky if I sneeze
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.47,0:00:09.65,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Some tea with honey from the bees
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.88,0:00:11.75,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Whenever you can brew it
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.09,0:00:12.84,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,I'll get your tea
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.21,0:00:15.31,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,And while I get a little rest
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.50,0:00:17.79,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,A teeny tiny small request
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.94,0:00:20.11,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Some codfish oil for my chest
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.30,0:00:22.21,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Poured from a crystal cruet
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.36,0:00:23.15,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,A crystal cruet?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.34,0:00:24.84,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,My goodness, I'm a nincompoop
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.99,0:00:26.45,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Because I fear I've got the croup
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.60,0:00:28.02,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,I need a vat of pumpkin soup
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.18,0:00:29.64,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,And scarves made out of zinnias
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.86,0:00:31.29,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Did I say zinnias? I meant silk
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.44,0:00:32.94,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Or something shiny of that ilk
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.09,0:00:34.48,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,And then I'll need some nice warm milk
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.62,0:00:36.01,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,And pastries from Abyssinia
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.16,0:00:37.66,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,And since my stomach's feeling crummy
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.81,0:00:39.16,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Why not give my aching tummy
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.31,0:00:40.62,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Something soothing, something yummy
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.77,0:00:41.98,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Piled up with noodles?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.24,0:00:43.36,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Add a slice of homemade rye
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.51,0:00:44.94,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,With stacks of Swiss way up high
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.09,0:00:46.36,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Served with sides of sweet mince pie
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.51,0:00:48.20,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,More basil; I need oodles!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.42,0:00:49.29,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Anything else?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.59,0:00:53.19,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,I'll be grateful for your charity
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.49,0:00:55.89,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Until the bitter end
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.52,0:00:59.64,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Because I've heard that tenderness
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.90,0:01:03.24,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Is what you lend an ailing friend
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.61,0:01:05.83,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Tenderness, isn't that right, friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.16,0:01:06.99,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Right, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.17,0:01:09.84,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,So, who's ready for my big reprise?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.21,0:01:11.60,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,I'd like that glass of water please
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.75,0:01:13.17,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Some magic spell to cure disease
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.33,0:01:14.71,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,A firm "gesundhoof" when I sneeze
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.86,0:01:16.25,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,A fresh bouquet of roses
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.40,0:01:17.86,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Some lozenges will soon appease
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.01,0:01:19.40,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,My wheezing when I start to sneeze
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.59,0:01:21.01,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,A wig to keep me from the breeze
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.16,0:01:22.59,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,And blankets for my toes-es
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.74,0:01:24.12,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Take tweezers out from my valise
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.28,0:01:25.51,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,And then massage my knobby knees
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.66,0:01:26.97,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,A bowl of peas, some extra cheese
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.12,0:01:28.29,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,A cuddle with a Pekingese
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.44,0:01:29.71,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,A singing harp who's named Louise
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.86,0:01:31.17,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,A goat on skis, a new trapeze
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.33,0:01:35.19,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,And more and more and more and more of these
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.83,0:01:37.25,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,And just because I oughta
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.47,0:01:40.29,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Make sure I'm drinking in the right
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.47,0:01:42.28,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Amount of fluids day and night
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.42,0:01:43.96,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,I wish I may, I wish I might
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.15,0:01:45.42,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Have just one little thing
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.61,0:01:46.81,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Oh, would you please finally bring
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.96,0:01:48.72,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Me that tiny glass
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.06,0:01:54.95,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Of water